title: What would you guys think of a "CopyCat" series.
body:
Its really hard to do anything unique to league right now.
The only thing I have to claim as  my own is "Helping Others Improve"

-----------------------------------

So what do you guys think if I created some Omage's (respect) to some other league youtubers.
And make videos as of they had actually made them.

doing one on solwolf will be easy, peace pidgeon I don't think I can do at my level.

What do you guys think, and who should I do them on?
